1.2.name: wordpress/cleanfrog
1.2.description: Custom Wordpress theme designed by Nearfrog Designs. It features two columns, fixed width with widget support in a clean layout consisting of grays, blue and orange. Also features collapsible widgets and Cufon text-replacement for the title.
